<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<h3>How much does exterior painting cost in Doncaster?</h3>
<p>Prices vary depending on surface condition and size, but most Doncaster homes fall between <strong>£250–£1,200</strong>. We always provide a free, no-obligation quote.</p>

<h3>What paints do you use?</h3>
<p>We primarily use <strong>Sandtex masonry paint</strong> for exterior walls and high-performance exterior wood coatings for fences, sheds and gates.</p>

<h3>Do you prepare the surfaces first?</h3>
<p>Yes, preparation is included. We clean, sand, scrape and prime surfaces to ensure a strong bond and long-lasting finish.</p>

<h3>Are you insured?</h3>
<p>Yes, we are fully insured for all residential and commercial exterior works.</p>

